parameters:
\n<Eury>Alright, I'll count to 30! Remember, no going to the east
area!
\n<Eury>Found you~? But you're not even hiding!
\n<Eury>(Could it be that they're being bullied...?)
\n<Eury>(If that's the case, I have to protect them!)
\n<Eury>It's okay, you can tell me anything!
\n<Child 1>I want Onee-san to do naughty things to me!!!
\n<Eury>Wait, wait a minute! That's not okay...!

\n<Child 1>I don't want to do it with three people like before, I want
to do it with just one!
\n<Eury>I won't play with you anymore if you keep this up!
\n<Child 1>Waaah! He got to fondle so much!
\n<Eury>No, it's not like that at all!

parameters.name: 【エロ（喘ぎ）10_02】じゅぶじゅぶフェラ音

parameters: \n<Eury>(If someone finds out we're doing this...)
\n<Child 1>Ah, I, I can't hold it anymore! It's coming out!!!
\n<Eury>(Such a large amount... you were really excited♡)
\n<Child 3>We thought you weren't coming to search at all...
\n<Child 2>Were you hogging the new Onee-san all to yourself?!
\n<Eury>No, it's not like that! This child isn't to blame...!
\n<Child 1>Here, this is for you... Onee-san, I'm sorry.

\n<child>Hey hey, if it's okay with you, do you want to play
together?
\n<Eury>(It seems fun, but it's a bit different from my mission...)
\n<child>Then, let me know when you're free! Anytime is fine!
